{
  "stem": "23540.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We haven't been as far, but we think about to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we think too long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't realize that it's so close to us, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't realize.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was standing outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And suddenly, the plane, you know, they started bombarding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not far from us was the [NON-ENGLISH], the army was standing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How do you call it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they started to bombard this-- this place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was not exactly-- but you can see from the distance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Later it was the war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We couldn't believe it, but it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my husband was in the army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They take him to army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he come to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I say, go and bring some gas mask.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because he say that we'll be-- and he run to bring-- before he come, I went away, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We take-- we have horses and errand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We couldn't take a car, but you take horses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we run away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He come, and I was-- I was not at home anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it's-- we go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We-- we travel.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I change the horses with the gypsies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The gypsies give me very bad horses, I give them the good one, but tired, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was not so easy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just-- we know the Germans coming this way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But whenever you go, the Germans come.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we stop and was bombarding in the meantime.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first, I tell you something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I go and I want to sleep in the hotel, when there was a little hotel, and I come in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I say to-- to the lady to show me the room, she show me, I said, this-- this seems not so clean.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the sheets are-- oh, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Only three officers were sleeping here a few days before.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
